author: @DouglasLima
content: Y’all out there… look at her, take a deep deep breath and repeat after me: THIS IS THE GIRL FROM RIO! Brazilian! From the roots. I saw this girl become a woman p, right in front of my eyes!  We’re same age, and I was there right beside her saying: I have gone far, but she’ll go further! She’s a piece of me, she’s a piece of US! WE EXIST! And honestly… WE ARE FUCKING GOOD! THANKS.
